metadata.description: i was reminiscing about summertime in Europe at my house a couple days ago with some friends and just remembering the way life felt at the time. since making these BREATHE ambient tracks i've been pretty much exclusively using my Prophet this week, so with this track i just had fun with it.

lyrics.text:
It’s all but done 

This summers over 

I’m heading home with foreign clothes and a fresh little sunburn 

We weren’t meant for long my little angel

Our time is up 

But if you don’t have plans for October 

Can we take it back down baby?

Can we take it back down to the amalfi coast where you held my body close 

Everything was fire

Can we take it back down baby?

Can we take it back?

Missing you across the pond 

Wish you could rewind the clocks

Get back all our time

It’s all but gone to California

Where it feels like the Fourth of July even in November 

I’m still in love

I thought once we’re sober that I’d come to my senses

But our sexual tensions not disappearing 

If you can feel it though

Can we take it back down baby?

Can we take it back down to the amalfi coast where you held my body close 

Everything was fire

Can we take it back down baby?

Can we take it back?

Missing you across the pond 

Wish you could rewind the clocks

Get back all our time

Can we take it back?

metadata.name: Take It Back #1
metadata.title: Take It Back
